<li>Facebook страницата <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/wordcampbg">WordCamp Bulgaria</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/events/726545920695515/">Събитието във Facebook</a></li>
